# ██╗░░██╗███████╗██╗░░░██╗  ██████╗░██╗███╗░░██╗██████╗░░██████╗
# ██║░██╔╝██╔════╝╚██╗░██╔╝  ██╔══██╗██║████╗░██║██╔══██╗██╔════╝
# █████═╝░█████╗░░░╚████╔╝░  ██████╦╝██║██╔██╗██║██║░░██║╚█████╗░
# ██╔═██╗░██╔══╝░░░░╚██╔╝░░  ██╔══██╗██║██║╚████║██║░░██║░╚═══██╗
# ██║░╚██╗███████╗░░░██║░░░  ██████╦╝██║██║░╚███║██████╔╝██████╔╝
# ╚═╝░░╚═╝╚══════╝░░░╚═╝░░░  ╚═════╝░╚═╝╚═╝░░╚══╝╚═════╝░╚═════╝░

SetEnv DIR Next

AddToFunc FocusRaiseAndStuff
+ I Iconify off
+ I Focus
+ I Raise

AddToFunc SwitchWindow
+ I $[DIR] (CurrentPage, !Iconic, !Sticky) FocusRaiseAndStuff
+ I Deschedule 134000
+ I PipeRead `[ "$[DIR]" == "Prev" ] && \
	echo 'SetEnv NDIR Next' || \
	echo 'SetEnv NDIR Prev'`
+ I Schedule 700 134000 SetEnv DIR $[NDIR]

Key Tab A 4  SwitchWindow

Silent Key Tab A M WindowList Root c c NoDeskSort, SelectOnRelease Meta_L

IgnoreModifiers L25

Key Return	A 4 	Exec 	termite	 		
Key c 		A 4		Exec 	wmctrl -xa google-chrome-stable || setsid google-chrome-stable          
Key n 		A 4 	Exec    wmctrl -xa nemo  || setsid -f nemo
Key s 		A 4 	Exec  	wmctrl -xa code || setsid -f code

Key XF86AudioRaiseVolume A A Exec pactl set-sink-volume 0 +5%  # > Volume +5
Key XF86AudioLowerVolume A A Exec pactl set-sink-volume 0 -5%  # > Volume -5
Key XF86AudioMute A A Exec pactl set-sink-mute 0 toggle 	   # > Volume Muted

DestroyFunc Thumbnail
AddToFunc Thumbnail
 
+ I ThisWindow (Shaded) WindowShade
+ I PipeRead 'bash $[scripts]/crthumb "$[w.id]" "$[cache]"'
  
DestroyFunc DeThumbnail
AddToFunc DeThumbnail
+ I PipeRead 'bash $[scripts]/dethumb "$[w.id]" "$[cache]"'
*FvwmEvent: deiconify DeThumbnail

Style * IconBox 1000x1000-145+180, IconGrid 1 1, \
IconFill top right, !IconTitle, IconBackgroundRelief 0

Key z A 4 Thumbnail
 
Key Print A 4 Exec exec scrot 'My_FVWM_%a-%d%b%y_%H.%M.png' -e 'viewnior ~/$f'
Key q WT 4 Close 			# Fecha a janela focada
Key space WT 4 Maximize		# Maximiza a janela focada -h -a -m  
Key space WT 4S ModuleSynchronous FvwmRearrange -tile -animate -h 0 0 0 92 -noresize -nostretch
Key a WT 4S Thumbnail		# Minimiza a janela focada em forma de thumbnail
Key r A 4S Restart 			# Restarta o jerenciador de janelas 
Key e A 4S Quit 			# Encerra a sessão
Key a A 4 WindowShade 		# Recolhe a janela focada para dentro da barra de titulos
 
Key 1 A 4 GotoDesk 0 0 
Key 2 A 4 GotoDesk 0 1
Key 3 A 4 GotoDesk 0 2
Key 4 A 4 GotoDesk 0 3
Key 5 A 4 GotoDesk 0 4
Key 6 A 4 GotoDesk 0 5
Key 7 A 4 GotoDesk 0 6
Key 8 A 4 GotoDesk 0 7
Key 9 A 4 GotoDesk 0 8
Key 0 A 4 GotoDesk 0 9
 
Key 1 A 4S MovetoDesk 0 0   # Move a janela em foco para a area de trabalho 1
Key 2 A 4S MovetoDesk 0 1	# Move a janela em foco para a area de trabalho 2
Key 3 A 4S MovetoDesk 0 2	# Move a janela em foco para a area de trabalho 3
Key 4 A 4S MovetoDesk 0 3   # Move a janela em foco para a area de trabalho 4
Key 5 A 4S MovetoDesk 0 4	# Move a janela em foco para a area de trabalho 5
Key 6 A 4S MovetoDesk 0 5 	# Move a janela em foco para a area de trabalho 6
Key 7 A 4S MovetoDesk 0 6	# Move a janela em foco para a area de trabalho 7
Key 8 A 4S MovetoDesk 0 7	# Move a janela em foco para a area de trabalho 8
Key 9 A 4S MovetoDesk 0 8	# Move a janela em foco para a area de trabalho 9
Key 0 A 4S MovetoDesk 0 9	# Move a janela em foco para a area de trabalho 10

AddToFunc SomeFunc
    + I SendToModule FvwmAnimate animate 20 25 15 10 44 23 6 12#
    + I Iconify
Mouse 1  A SomeFunc

Key Left A 4S TileLeft 		# Divide a janela em foco no lado esquerdo da tela
Key Right A 4S TileRight		# Divide a janela em foco no lado direto da tela
Key Up A 4S TileTop			# Divide a janela em foco no lado superior da tela
Key Down A 4S TileBottom 	# Divide a janela em foco no lado inferior da tela

Key Up A 4 TileTopLeft
Key Right A 4 TileTopRight 
Key Left A 4 TileBottomLeft 
Key Down A 4 TileBottomRight 

DestroyFunc CenterWindow
AddToFunc   CenterWindow
+ I ThisWindow Piperead "echo Move \
      $(( $[vp.width]/2-$[w.width]/2 ))p \
      $(( $[vp.height]/2-$[w.height]/2 ))p"

DestroyFunc ResizeCenter
AddToFunc ResizeCenter
+ "I" Resize $0 $1 $2
+ "I" CenterWindow

Key Up A C4 ResizeCenter br keep w-1
Key Down A C4 ResizeCenter br keep w+1
Key Left A C4 ResizeCenter br w+1 w-1
Key Right A C4 ResizeCenter br w-1 w+1
